org.apache.commons.functor.core.comparator

Class IsLessThanOrEqual<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.commons.functor.core.comparator.IsLessThanOrEqual<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the binary predicate input types
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, BinaryFunctor<T,T>, BinaryPredicate<T,T>, Functor

    public final class IsLessThanOrEqual<T>
extends Object
implements BinaryPredicate<T,T>, Serializable
    A BinaryPredicate that tests true iff the left argument is less than or equal to the right argument under the specified Comparator. When no (or a null Comparator is specified, a Comparable Comparator is used.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1365328 $ $Date: 2012-07-24 19:19:23 -0300 (Tue, 24 Jul 2012) $
